videoSnippet.title: Magnus Carlsen Sticks his Tongue out and Laughs as he Tricks Grischuk
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Happy Birthday Magnus Carlsen!

Legendary chess game. Grischuk is leading 2-0 in the match. This is game 3, and Carlsen's position isn't really something. But here things get interesting :)

Alexander Grischuk vs Magnus Carlsen
Chess.com Speedchess Championship 2016
